com.loyauty.service.init
Class ConfigServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.loyauty.service.ServiceImpl
      com.loyauty.service.init.ConfigServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConfigService, Service
public class ConfigServiceImpl
extends ServiceImpl
implements ConfigService

Main configuration service on GameJab. The service loads application-wide configuration from properties files and exposes a unique entry point for all other services. This service should be initialized on application startup since other subsystems functionalities depend on it.

Author:
Muthanna
